snippet.textDisplay:
I’ve been watching for more than 5 years so it’s not exactly day one but I was younger then. I was only 12 and now I’m 17 so when you think about it I’ve been watching since I was a kid, and even though I’ve been watching people like Markiplier and JackSepticEye for a longer time, I feel like Cory had a special effect on who I became and how I grew up you know? Like his videos hit different, his attitude and mindset. I’m just glad to be one of the lucky people who watched him since youth and haven given up on him not ONCE even when he took his breaks (like the 9 month one which just came back from 2 days ago). Not only is he blessed to have us as a community as he mentioned but we’re blessed to have him as a leader and for some (like myself) an older brother❤️.

(This is a comment I posted on another one of his videos from 5 years ago and I just posted as a reply to someone else’s comment)
